---
// PrytulaUSA.astro
---

<section class="usa-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">PRYTULA<br>FOUNDATION<br>USA</h2>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="badge">501(c)(3) NONPROFIT</div>

      <p class="text-block">
        Prytula Foundation U.S.A. is a recognized <strong>501(c)(3) nonprofit</strong>, established in 2024
        in Chicago, Illinois. We focus specifically on healthcare and kids projects, as well as humanitarian
        demining programs.
      </p>

      <div class="stats-row">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-value">$5.7M</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Raised in 2024</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-value">$5.4M</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Direct Aid Provided</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-block">
        For full details, please check our Annual Report, Auditors Report and 990 Form on our website.
      </p>

      <a href="https://prytulafoundation.us" class="usa-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Visit prytulafoundation.us â†’
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .usa-section {
    background: var(--bg-white);
    padding: var(--section-padding-y) var(--section-padding-x);
    color: var(--text-black);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: var(--container-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-section-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-black);
    line-height: var(--leading-section-lg);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-section-lg);
  }

  .content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--paragraph-gap);
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--bg-blue);
    color: var(--text-white);
    font-size: var(--text-body-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-black);
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-body);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    align-self: flex-start;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .text-block {
    font-size: var(--text-body-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-body);
  }

  .text-block strong {
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
  }

  .stats-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: var(--text-heading-md);
    font-weight: var(--font-black);
    line-height: var(--leading-heading-md);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-heading-md);
    color: var(--color-blue);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-gray);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .usa-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-body-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-black);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-body);
    color: var(--color-blue);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .usa-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .usa-section {
      padding: var(--section-padding-y-mobile) var(--section-padding-x);
    }

    .container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .stats-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
